---
---
<section class="relative pt-40 pb-24 px-4 bg-[#FFFEFC] text-center overflow-hidden">
  <!-- Watermark sutil — "AI" e "Clin" posicionados como no Figma -->
  <div class="watermark-bg absolute inset-0 pointer-events-none select-none" aria-hidden="true">
    <span class="absolute font-extrabold text-[#0F3E17] leading-none" style="font-size: clamp(120px, 18vw, 260px); left: 28%; top: 28%; transform: translateY(-50%);">AI</span>
    <span class="absolute font-light text-[#0F3E17] leading-none" style="font-size: clamp(120px, 18vw, 260px); left: 44%; top: 32%; transform: translateY(-50%);">Clin</span>
  </div>

  <div class="max-w-[860px] mx-auto relative z-10">
    <!-- Tag -->
    <div class="reveal inline-flex items-center px-3 py-1.5 rounded-full bg-[#E1F4DF] mb-6">
      <span class="text-[0.75rem] font-semibold tracking-[0.08em] uppercase text-[#0F3E17]">
        AIClin — Infraestrutura de IA para Clínicas
      </span>
    </div>

    <!-- Headline -->
    <h1 class="reveal reveal-delay-1 text-[2.75rem] sm:text-[3.75rem] lg:text-[5rem] font-light leading-[1.1] tracking-[-0.02em] text-[#0F3E17] mb-6">
      Sua clínica perde até<br class="hidden sm:block"> R$&nbsp;50&nbsp;mil por ano<br class="hidden sm:block">
      com faltas e má gestão<br class="hidden sm:block">
      <span style="opacity: 0.55;">— e dá para resolver isso.</span>
    </h1>

    <!-- Subtítulo -->
    <p class="reveal reveal-delay-2 text-[1.0625rem] leading-[1.8] text-[rgba(15,62,23,0.65)] max-w-[600px] mx-auto mb-10">
      Implementamos um sistema completo de agendamento automático, confirmação e reativação de pacientes. Sem mudar o software que você usa. Sem treinamento longo.
    </p>

    <!-- CTAs -->
    <div class="reveal reveal-delay-3 flex flex-col sm:flex-row items-center justify-center gap-3">
      <a
        href="#cta-final"
        class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 px-6 py-4 bg-[#0F3E17] text-white text-base font-medium rounded-[12px] hover:opacity-90 transition-opacity duration-300 min-h-[52px]"
      >
        Agendar análise gratuita
        <svg width="16" height="16" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" aria-hidden="true">
          <path d="M5 12h14M12 5l7 7-7 7"/>
        </svg>
      </a>
      <a
        href="#como-funciona"
        class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 px-6 py-4 text-[#0F3E17] text-base font-medium rounded-[12px] border border-[#0F3E17] hover:bg-[#E1F4DF] transition-colors duration-300 min-h-[52px]"
      >
        Ver como funciona
      </a>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .watermark-bg {
    opacity: 0.05;
  }

  @media (prefers-reduced-motion: no-preference) {
    .watermark-bg {
      animation: wm-in 1.6s cubic-bezier(0.16, 1, 0.3, 1) 0.2s both;
    }

    @keyframes wm-in {
      from {
        opacity: 0;
        transform: translateY(8px);
      }
      to {
        opacity: 0.05;
        transform: translateY(0);
      }
    }
  }
</style>
